          learning with scalable architectures. From LLM integrations and sentiment analysis systems to API design
          and cloud deployments, I bridge intelligent models with real-world business applications.
        </p>
        <p class="bio-text">
          Currently working on AI-driven sentiment analysis platforms, automation systems, and scalable backend
          infrastructures.
        </p>
